aces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween 話到明係亂諗野仲點會向好嗰邊諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add7e7e8349958b6dde37d0c9f0370bd7f966149","tid":339124,"uid":55866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係，唸得愈多愈傷心</blockquote><br />\n人地仲要實牙實齒咁講，<br />\n但其實明知對方呃你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踢爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87882cb8a2dbb0cc63c01937668c82ab9794a461","tid":339124,"uid":110266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T18:59:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係，唸得愈多愈傷心</blockquote><br />\n人地仲要實牙實齒咁講，<br />\n但其實明知對方呃你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n踢爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉，佢到時又死兜爛兜，<br />\n又喊又盛，我都廢事煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45efb0a5f251f1bd93f5c00941a034c89377e11d","tid":339124,"uid":110266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>然後就會亂諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n驚其實仲有更加多野呃你，<br />\n但你唔知</blockquote><br />\n佢成日叫我要向好嗰邊諗<br />\n但係好嗰邊根本連自己都說服唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbetween 話到明係亂諗野仲點會向好嗰邊諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都幾sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6ad1716d4e95ef1db8755025611c352d835d1e","tid":339124,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T19:09:07.000Z","msg":"係咁而問一兩句 自己心入面知咩事就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687c05e6c507bf0d68117eaff5d15f43b4c34af7"